<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the system was set up correctly and link training was successful.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE otherwise.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
